svg.title: Green Rocket
svg.desc: GREEN ROCKET is the first crowdinvesting platform specializing in sustainable energy, environment, mobility and healthcare companies. Everyone has the opportunity to invest online in selected companies (equity-based crowdfunding) and benefit from their growth. The variety of investment opportunities extends from startups and first-stage companies to project financing of established companies. As a crowd investor, you are a venture capitalist and manage your own portfolio of attractive, promising projects.
